  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Engineer (with own Vehicle)",
  "description": "<p>Sales Engineer (Must have own vehicle) (D2)<br />$2800-$4000<br />Mon-Thu 8am-6pm, Fri 8am-5.30pm<br />Sat, Sun & PH off<br /><br />Car allowance $800<br />Company provide petrol card<br />Location at Tuas & Loyang<br />-Bonus<br />-After confirmation increment<br />-Yearly increment<br />-12 days annual leave (Max 16 days)<br />-Medical benefits<br /><br /><strong>Jobs & Responsibilities:</strong><br />1. Maintain existing customers' accounts and resourceful in developing new accounts.<br />2. Respond to customers' enquiries, follow-up and provide technical solutions to clients.<br />3. Compiling and review contractual quotation for existing and new products as per customer's enquiries.<br />4. Provide regular update to customers on project development in a timely manner.<br />5. Work closely among inter-departments to ensure committed schedules are met.<br />6. Prepare monthly sales input / output and having keen interest and confident in pursuing sales targets.<br />7. Initiate and develop good customer service and rapport with customer and always to serve customer.<br />8. Analyse profit / loss projects and providing cost control and cost effectiveness strategy.<br />9. Participate the implementation of risk assessment and risk control of medical devices.<br /><br /><strong>Competence Requirements:</strong><br />1. Preferred to have NTC / Diploma in Mechanical / Manufacturing Engineering field or equivalent.<br />2. Preferably with 3 to 6 years relevant experience and proven track record in industrial sales and contract manufacturing industry.<br />3. Preference to be given to those with work experience in CNC Precision Engineering / Fabrication / Sheetmetal Industry.<br />4. Customer driven, result oriented, resourceful and independent.<br />5. Possess excellent interpersonal communication skills and is an effective team player who is also self driven wih a strong achievement orientation.<br />6. Must possess class 3 driving license and own vehicle.</p>",
